---
title: Hoisin-Glazed Veggie Burger with Beyond Meat® and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Sweet and aromatic hoisin makes an exciting swap for traditional BBQ sauce. Cool and crunchy cucumbers, zesty green onions and wholesome spring mix are layered with a hearty Beyond Meat® patty for a fresh take on a burger supper!
